            "content": "<p>craftsmanship, transform these diamonds into heirlooms meant to be cherished forever.<br/><br/>At Lucira Jewelry, every creation embodies our promise: crafted to last, designed to shine. Explore our curated<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/earrings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> earrings</span></a> and<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/earrings-for-men\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> earrings for men</span></a> for timeless pieces.</p>",
